Use the standard library
This is how to motto ^^:
   The answer is "今日もがんばろう"
Now you know
>>> motto, do it 
"今日もがんばろう"
This is how to greet of name:
   The answer is "こんにちは、{name}さん！"
Now you know
>>> greet of "ゆい" 
"こんにちは、ゆいさん！"
This is how to score_msg of name and points:
   The answer is "{name}さんのスコアは{points}点です"
Now you know
>>> score_msg of "太郎" and 95 
"太郎さんのスコアは95点です"
>>> tostring of 42 
"42"